{
  "video_id": "b8z6HfSq7l8",
  "title": "Why our universe might exist on a knife-edge | Gian Giudice",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13179.0,
      "end_time": 15523.0,
      "text": "So last year, on the Fourth of July,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15523.0,
      "end_time": 18022.0,
      "text": "experiments at the Large Hadron Collider"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18022.0,
      "end_time": 20312.0,
      "text": "discovered the Higgs boson."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 20312.0,
      "end_time": 22280.0,
      "text": "It was a historical day."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22280.0,
      "end_time": 24575.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s no doubt that from now on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24575.0,
      "end_time": 26409.0,
      "text": "the Fourth of July will be remembered"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 26409.0,
      "end_time": 28851.0,
      "text": "not as the day of the Declaration of Independence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 28851.0,
      "end_time": 32685.0,
      "text": "but as the day of the discovery of the Higgs boson."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32685.000000000004,
      "end_time": 35117.0,
      "text": "Well, at least, here at CERN."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 35117.0,
      "end_time": 39272.0,
      "text": "But for me, the biggest surprise of that day"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39272.0,
      "end_time": 41771.0,
      "text": "was that there was no big surprise."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 41771.0,
      "end_time": 44370.0,
      "text": "In the eye of a theoretical physicist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 44370.0,
      "end_time": 46263.0,
      "text": "the Higgs boson is a clever explanation"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 46263.0,
      "end_time": 49786.0,
      "text": "of how some elementary particles gain mass,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 49786.0,
      "end_time": 52622.0,
      "text": "but it seems a fairly unsatisfactory"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 52622.0,
      "end_time": 54828.0,
      "text": "and incomplete solution."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 54828.0,
      "end_time": 57852.0,
      "text": "Too many questions are left unanswered."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 57852.0,
      "end_time": 60687.0,
      "text": "The Higgs boson does not share the beauty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 60687.0,
      "end_time": 62572.0,
      "text": "the symmetry, the elegance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 62572.0,
      "end_time": 65300.0,
      "text": "of the rest of the elementary particle world."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 65300.0,
      "end_time": 68922.0,
      "text": "For this reason, the majority of theoretical physicists"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 68922.0,
      "end_time": 71864.0,
      "text": "believe that the Higgs boson could not"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 71864.0,
      "end_time": 74346.0,
      "text": "be the full story."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 74346.0,
      "end_time": 77200.0,
      "text": "We were expecting new particles and new phenomena"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 77200.0,
      "end_time": 79650.0,
      "text": "accompanying the Higgs boson."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 79650.0,
      "end_time": 81968.0,
      "text": "Instead, so far, the measurements"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 81968.0,
      "end_time": 85726.0,
      "text": "coming from the LHC show no signs of new particles"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 85726.0,
      "end_time": 87875.0,
      "text": "or unexpected phenomena."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 87875.0,
      "end_time": 91528.0,
      "text": "Of course, the verdict is not definitive."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 91528.0,
      "end_time": 95522.0,
      "text": "In 2015, the LHC will almost double"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 95522.0,
      "end_time": 98213.0,
      "text": "the energy of the colliding protons,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 98213.0,
      "end_time": 100284.0,
      "text": "and these more powerful collisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 100284.0,
      "end_time": 104868.0,
      "text": "will allow us to explore further the particle world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 104868.0,
      "end_time": 108000.0,
      "text": "and we will certainly learn much more."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 108000.0,
      "end_time": 111146.0,
      "text": "But for the moment, since we have found"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 111146.0,
      "end_time": 114295.0,
      "text": "no evidence for new phenomena, let us suppose"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 114295.0,
      "end_time": 117459.0,
      "text": "that the particles that we know today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 117459.0,
      "end_time": 119315.0,
      "text": "including the Higgs boson,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 119315.0,
      "end_time": 122600.0,
      "text": "are the only elementary particles in nature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 122600.0,
      "end_time": 125344.0,
      "text": "even at energies much larger"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 125344.0,
      "end_time": 128110.0,
      "text": "than what we have explored so far."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 128110.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132742.0,
      "text": "Let&#39;s see where this hypothesis is going to lead us."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 132742.0,
      "end_time": 136174.0,
      "text": "We will find a surprising and intriguing result"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 136174.0,
      "end_time": 139973.0,
      "text": "about our universe, and to explain my point,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 139973.0,
      "end_time": 143849.0,
      "text": "let me first tell you what the Higgs is about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 143849.0,
      "end_time": 146983.0,
      "text": "and to do so, we have to go back"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 146983.0,
      "end_time": 151340.0,
      "text": "to one tenth of a billionth of a second"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 151340.0,
      "end_time": 152871.0,
      "text": "after the Big Bang."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 152871.0,
      "end_time": 154912.0,
      "text": "And according to the Higgs theory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 154912.0,
      "end_time": 158278.0,
      "text": "at that instant, a dramatic event took place"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 158278.0,
      "end_time": 159869.0,
      "text": "in the universe."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 159869.0,
      "end_time": 164660.0,
      "text": "Space-time underwent a phase transition."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 164660.0,
      "end_time": 167737.0,
      "text": "It was something very similar to the phase transition"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 167737.0,
      "end_time": 171282.0,
      "text": "that occurs when water turns into ice"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 171282.0,
      "end_time": 173243.0,
      "text": "below zero degrees."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 173243.0,
      "end_time": 176183.0,
      "text": "But in our case, the phase transition"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 176183.0,
      "end_time": 178714.0,
      "text": "is not a change in the way the molecules"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 178714.0,
      "end_time": 181000.0,
      "text": "are arranged inside the material,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 181000.0,
      "end_time": 182888.0,
      "text": "but is about a change"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 182888.0,
      "end_time": 186514.0,
      "text": "of the very fabric of space-time."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 186514.0,
      "end_time": 189140.0,
      "text": "During this phase transition, empty space"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 189140.0,
      "end_time": 191812.0,
      "text": "became filled with a substance"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 191812.0,
      "end_time": 194844.0,
      "text": "that we now call Higgs field."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 194844.0,
      "end_time": 197173.0,
      "text": "And this substance may seem invisible to us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 197173.0,
      "end_time": 199851.0,
      "text": "but it has a physical reality."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 199851.0,
      "end_time": 201909.0,
      "text": "It surrounds us all the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 201909.0,
      "end_time": 205610.0,
      "text": "just like the air we breathe in this room."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 205610.0,
      "end_time": 207928.0,
      "text": "And some elementary particles interact"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 207928.0,
      "end_time": 211756.0,
      "text": "with this substance, gaining energy in the process."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 211756.0,
      "end_time": 214831.0,
      "text": "And this intrinsic energy is what we call"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 214831.0,
      "end_time": 216964.0,
      "text": "the mass of a particle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 216964.0,
      "end_time": 220217.0,
      "text": "and by discovering the Higgs boson, the LHC"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 220217.0,
      "end_time": 224749.0,
      "text": "has conclusively proved that this substance is real,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 224749.0,
      "end_time": 228668.0,
      "text": "because it is the stuff the Higgs bosons are made of."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 228668.0,
      "end_time": 232112.0,
      "text": "And this, in a nutshell, is the essence of the Higgs story."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 232112.0,
      "end_time": 236855.0,
      "text": "But this story is far more interesting than that."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 236855.0,
      "end_time": 239166.0,
      "text": "By studying the Higgs theory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 239166.0,
      "end_time": 241526.0,
      "text": "theoretical physicists discovered,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 241526.0,
      "end_time": 243430.0,
      "text": "not through an experiment"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 243430.0,
      "end_time": 245906.0,
      "text": "but with the power of mathematics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 245906.0,
      "end_time": 249618.0,
      "text": "that the Higgs field does not necessarily exist"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 249618.0,
      "end_time": 252955.0,
      "text": "only in the form that we observe today."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 252955.0,
      "end_time": 258000.0,
      "text": "Just like matter can exist as liquid or solid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 258000.0,
      "end_time": 262572.0,
      "text": "so the Higgs field, the substance that fills all space-time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 262572.0,
      "end_time": 265926.0,
      "text": "could exist in two states."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 265926.0,
      "end_time": 268236.0,
      "text": "Besides the known Higgs state,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 268236.0,
      "end_time": 271383.0,
      "text": "there could be a second state in which the Higgs field"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 271383.0,
      "end_time": 274919.0,
      "text": "is billions and billions times denser"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 274919.0,
      "end_time": 276964.0,
      "text": "than what we observe today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 276964.0,
      "end_time": 280451.0,
      "text": "and the mere existence of another state"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 280451.0,
      "end_time": 284696.0,
      "text": "of the Higgs field poses a potential problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 284696.0,
      "end_time": 287934.0,
      "text": "This is because, according to the laws"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 287934.0,
      "end_time": 290627.0,
      "text": "of quantum mechanics, it is possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 290627.0,
      "end_time": 293459.0,
      "text": "to have transitions between two states,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 293459.0,
      "end_time": 296408.0,
      "text": "even in the presence of an energy barrier"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 296408.0,
      "end_time": 299036.0,
      "text": "separating the two states,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 299036.0,
      "end_time": 301245.0,
      "text": "and the phenomenon is called,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 301245.0,
      "end_time": 305387.0,
      "text": "quite appropriately, quantum tunneling."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 305387.0,
      "end_time": 307278.0,
      "text": "Because of quantum tunneling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 307278.0,
      "end_time": 309811.0,
      "text": "I could disappear from this room"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 309811.0,
      "end_time": 313133.0,
      "text": "and reappear in the next room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 313133.0,
      "end_time": 316528.0,
      "text": "practically penetrating the wall."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 316528.0,
      "end_time": 319343.0,
      "text": "But don&#39;t expect me to actually perform the trick"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 319343.0,
      "end_time": 321921.0,
      "text": "in front of your eyes, because the probability"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 321921.0,
      "end_time": 326309.0,
      "text": "for me to penetrate the wall is ridiculously small."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 326309.0,
      "end_time": 328907.0,
      "text": "You would have to wait a really long time"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 328907.0,
      "end_time": 331039.0,
      "text": "before it happens, but believe me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 331039.0,
      "end_time": 334216.0,
      "text": "quantum tunneling is a real phenomenon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 334216.0,
      "end_time": 337411.0,
      "text": "and it has been observed in many systems."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 337411.0,
      "end_time": 339973.0,
      "text": "For instance, the tunnel diode,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 339973.0,
      "end_time": 342170.0,
      "text": "a component used in electronics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 342170.0,
      "end_time": 344592.0,
      "text": "works thanks to the wonders"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 344592.0,
      "end_time": 346912.0,
      "text": "of quantum tunneling."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 346912.0,
      "end_time": 349204.0,
      "text": "But let&#39;s go back to the Higgs field."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 349204.0,
      "end_time": 353767.0,
      "text": "If the ultra-dense Higgs state existed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 353767.0,
      "end_time": 356121.0,
      "text": "then, because of quantum tunneling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 356121.0,
      "end_time": 359834.0,
      "text": "a bubble of this state could suddenly appear"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 359834.0,
      "end_time": 363076.0,
      "text": "in a certain place of the universe at a certain time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 363076.0,
      "end_time": 366841.0,
      "text": "and it is analogous to what happens when you boil water."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 366841.0,
      "end_time": 369930.0,
      "text": "Bubbles of vapor form inside the water,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 369930.0,
      "end_time": 373786.0,
      "text": "then they expand, turning liquid into gas."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 373786.0,
      "end_time": 378590.0,
      "text": "In the same way, a bubble of the ultra-dense Higgs state"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 378590.0,
      "end_time": 382017.0,
      "text": "could come into existence because of quantum tunneling."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 382017.0,
      "end_time": 384854.0,
      "text": "The bubble would then expand at the speed of light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 384854.0,
      "end_time": 388340.0,
      "text": "invading all space, and turning the Higgs field"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 388340.0,
      "end_time": 391989.0,
      "text": "from the familiar state into a new state."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 391989.0,
      "end_time": 396150.0,
      "text": "Is this a problem? Yes, it&#39;s a big a problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 396150.0,
      "end_time": 398895.0,
      "text": "We may not realize it in ordinary life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 398895.0,
      "end_time": 402100.0,
      "text": "but the intensity of the Higgs field is critical"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 402100.0,
      "end_time": 404745.0,
      "text": "for the structure of matter."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 404745.0,
      "end_time": 408818.0,
      "text": "If the Higgs field were only a few times more intense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 408818.0,
      "end_time": 411762.0,
      "text": "we would see atoms shrinking, neutrons decaying"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 411762.0,
      "end_time": 415448.0,
      "text": "inside atomic nuclei, nuclei disintegrating,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 415448.0,
      "end_time": 417788.0,
      "text": "and hydrogen would be"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 417788.0,
      "end_time": 422140.0,
      "text": "the only possible chemical element in the universe."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 422140.0,
      "end_time": 425151.0,
      "text": "And the Higgs field, in the ultra-dense Higgs state,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 425151.0,
      "end_time": 428965.0,
      "text": "is not just a few times more intense than today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 428965.0,
      "end_time": 431160.0,
      "text": "but billions of times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 431160.0,
      "end_time": 434362.0,
      "text": "and if space-time were filled by this Higgs state,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 434362.0,
      "end_time": 437515.0,
      "text": "all atomic matter would collapse."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 437515.0,
      "end_time": 442005.0,
      "text": "No molecular structures would be possible, no life."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 442005.0,
      "end_time": 445343.0,
      "text": "So, I wonder, is it possible"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 445343.0,
      "end_time": 447929.0,
      "text": "that in the future, the Higgs field"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 447929.0,
      "end_time": 450494.0,
      "text": "will undergo a phase transition and,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 450494.0,
      "end_time": 453623.0,
      "text": "through quantum tunneling, will be transformed"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 453623.0,
      "end_time": 458310.0,
      "text": "into this nasty, ultra-dense state?"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 458310.0,
      "end_time": 461835.0,
      "text": "In other words, I ask myself, what is the fate"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 461835.0,
      "end_time": 464918.0,
      "text": "of the Higgs field in our universe?"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 464918.0,
      "end_time": 467169.0,
      "text": "And the crucial ingredient necessary"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 467169.0,
      "end_time": 471555.0,
      "text": "to answer this question is the Higgs boson mass."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 471555.0,
      "end_time": 475666.0,
      "text": "And experiments at the LHC found that the mass"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 475666.0,
      "end_time": 479940.0,
      "text": "of the Higgs boson is about 126 GeV."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 479940.0,
      "end_time": 482976.0,
      "text": "This is tiny when expressed in familiar units,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 482976.0,
      "end_time": 484296.0,
      "text": "because it&#39;s equal to something like"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 484296.0,
      "end_time": 486503.0,
      "text": "10 to the minus 22 grams,"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 486503.0,
      "end_time": 490473.0,
      "text": "but it is large in particle physics units,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 490473.0,
      "end_time": 492577.0,
      "text": "because it is equal to the weight"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 492577.0,
      "end_time": 494823.0,
      "text": "of an entire molecule"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 494823.0,
      "end_time": 497243.0,
      "text": "of a DNA constituent."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 497243.0,
      "end_time": 500630.0,
      "text": "So armed with this information from the LHC,"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 500630.0,
      "end_time": 502574.0,
      "text": "together with some colleagues here at CERN,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 502574.0,
      "end_time": 504483.0,
      "text": "we computed the probability"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 504483.0,
      "end_time": 507498.0,
      "text": "that our universe could quantum tunnel"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 507498.0,
      "end_time": 510616.0,
      "text": "into the ultra-dense Higgs state,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 510616.0,
      "end_time": 514293.0,
      "text": "and we found a very intriguing result."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 514293.0,
      "end_time": 516442.0,
      "text": "Our calculations showed"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 516442.0,
      "end_time": 519614.0,
      "text": "that the measured value of the Higgs boson mass"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 519614.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521459.00000000006,
      "text": "is very special."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 521458.99999999994,
      "end_time": 524378.0,
      "text": "It has just the right value"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 524378.0,
      "end_time": 527071.0,
      "text": "to keep the universe hanging"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 527071.0,
      "end_time": 529641.0,
      "text": "in an unstable situation."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 529641.0,
      "end_time": 532897.0,
      "text": "The Higgs field is in a wobbly configuration"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 532897.0,
      "end_time": 534946.0,
      "text": "that has lasted so far"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 534946.0,
      "end_time": 537991.0,
      "text": "but that will eventually collapse."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 537991.0,
      "end_time": 541170.0,
      "text": "So according to these calculations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 541170.0,
      "end_time": 543200.0,
      "text": "we are like campers"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 543200.0,
      "end_time": 545652.0,
      "text": "who accidentally set their tent"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 545652.0,
      "end_time": 547446.0,
      "text": "at the edge of a cliff."
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 547446.0,
      "end_time": 549236.0,
      "text": "And eventually, the Higgs field"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 549236.0,
      "end_time": 551172.0,
      "text": "will undergo a phase transition"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 551172.0,
      "end_time": 554216.0,
      "text": "and matter will collapse into itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 554216.0,
      "end_time": 557660.0,
      "text": "So is this how humanity is going to disappear?"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 557660.0,
      "end_time": 559415.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t think so."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 559415.0,
      "end_time": 562768.0,
      "text": "Our calculation shows that quantum tunneling"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 562768.0,
      "end_time": 566424.0,
      "text": "of the Higgs field is not likely to occur"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 566424.0,
      "end_time": 569928.0,
      "text": "in the next 10 to the 100 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 569928.0,
      "end_time": 572970.0,
      "text": "and this is a very long time."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 572970.0,
      "end_time": 574738.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s even longer than"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 574738.0,
      "end_time": 578407.0,
      "text": "the time it takes for Italy to form a stable government."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 578407.0,
      "end_time": 580814.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 580814.0,
      "end_time": 584605.0,
      "text": "Even so, we will be long gone by then."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 584605.0,
      "end_time": 587213.0,
      "text": "In about five billion years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 587213.0,
      "end_time": 589670.0,
      "text": "our sun will become a red giant,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 589670.0,
      "end_time": 592183.0,
      "text": "as large as the Earth&#39;s orbit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 592183.0,
      "end_time": 595460.0,
      "text": "and our Earth will be kaput,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 595460.0,
      "end_time": 597817.0,
      "text": "and in a thousand billion years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 597817.0,
      "end_time": 600103.0,
      "text": "if dark energy keeps on fueling"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 600103.0,
      "end_time": 602938.0,
      "text": "space expansion at the present rate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 602938.0,
      "end_time": 607115.0,
      "text": "you will not even be able to see as far as your toes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 607115.0,
      "end_time": 608812.0,
      "text": "because everything around you"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 608812.0,
      "end_time": 612513.0,
      "text": "expands at a rate faster than the speed of light."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 612513.0,
      "end_time": 614498.0,
      "text": "So it is really unlikely"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 614498.0,
      "end_time": 618368.0,
      "text": "that we will be around to see the Higgs field collapse."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 618368.0,
      "end_time": 621947.0,
      "text": "But the reason why I am interested"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 621947.0,
      "end_time": 623959.0,
      "text": "in the transition of the Higgs field"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 623959.0,
      "end_time": 627244.0,
      "text": "is because I want to address the question,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 627244.0,
      "end_time": 632209.0,
      "text": "why is the Higgs boson mass so special?"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 632209.0,
      "end_time": 635183.0,
      "text": "Why is it just right to keep the universe"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 635183.0,
      "end_time": 638673.0,
      "text": "at the edge of a phase transition?"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 638673.0,
      "end_time": 642535.0,
      "text": "Theoretical physicists always ask &quot;why&quot; questions."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 642535.0,
      "end_time": 645210.0,
      "text": "More than how a phenomenon works,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 645210.0,
      "end_time": 647682.0,
      "text": "theoretical physicists are always interested in"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 647682.0,
      "end_time": 650914.0,
      "text": "why a phenomenon works in the way it works."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 650914.0,
      "end_time": 654276.0,
      "text": "We think that this these &quot;why&quot; questions"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 654276.0,
      "end_time": 655999.0,
      "text": "can give us clues"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 655999.0,
      "end_time": 659537.0,
      "text": "about the fundamental principles of nature."
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 659537.0,
      "end_time": 663442.0,
      "text": "And indeed, a possible answer to my question"
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 663442.0,
      "end_time": 667806.0,
      "text": "opens up new universes, literally."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 667806.0,
      "end_time": 671247.0,
      "text": "It has been speculated that our universe"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 671247.0,
      "end_time": 675380.0,
      "text": "is only a bubble in a soapy multiverse"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 675380.0,
      "end_time": 677943.0,
      "text": "made out of a multitude of bubbles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 677943.0,
      "end_time": 680159.0,
      "text": "and each bubble is a different universe"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 680159.0,
      "end_time": 682053.0,
      "text": "with different fundamental constants"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 682053.0,
      "end_time": 683918.0,
      "text": "and different physical laws."
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 683918.0,
      "end_time": 685924.0,
      "text": "And in this context, you can only talk about"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 685924.0,
      "end_time": 690635.0,
      "text": "the probability of finding a certain value of the Higgs mass."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 690635.0,
      "end_time": 692978.0,
      "text": "Then the key to the mystery"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 692978.0,
      "end_time": 696241.0,
      "text": "could lie in the statistical properties"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 696241.0,
      "end_time": 698469.0,
      "text": "of the multiverse."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 698469.0,
      "end_time": 700883.0,
      "text": "It would be something like what happens"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 700883.0,
      "end_time": 703120.0,
      "text": "with sand dunes on a beach."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 703120.0,
      "end_time": 705992.0,
      "text": "In principle, you could imagine to find sand dunes"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 705992.0,
      "end_time": 708422.0,
      "text": "of any slope angle in a beach,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 708422.0,
      "end_time": 712583.0,
      "text": "and yet, the slope angles of sand dunes"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 712583.0,
      "end_time": 716053.0,
      "text": "are typically around 30, 35 degrees."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 716053.0,
      "end_time": 717721.0,
      "text": "And the reason is simple:"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 717721.0,
      "end_time": 721399.0,
      "text": "because wind builds up the sand, gravity makes it fall."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 721399.0,
      "end_time": 724283.0,
      "text": "As a result, the vast majority of sand dunes"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 724283.0,
      "end_time": 728202.0,
      "text": "have slope angles around the critical value,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 728202.0,
      "end_time": 730186.0,
      "text": "near to collapse."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 730186.0,
      "end_time": 733183.0,
      "text": "And something similar could happen"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 733183.0,
      "end_time": 737720.0,
      "text": "for the Higgs boson mass in the multiverse."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 737720.0,
      "end_time": 740592.0,
      "text": "In the majority of bubble universes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 740592.0,
      "end_time": 743649.0,
      "text": "the Higgs mass could be around the critical value,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 743649.0,
      "end_time": 747245.0,
      "text": "near to a cosmic collapse of the Higgs field,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 747245.0,
      "end_time": 749192.0,
      "text": "because of two competing effects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 749192.0,
      "end_time": 752778.0,
      "text": "just as in the case of sand."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 752778.0,
      "end_time": 755923.0,
      "text": "My story does not have an end,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 755923.0,
      "end_time": 759658.0,
      "text": "because we still don&#39;t know the end of the story."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 759658.0,
      "end_time": 762946.0,
      "text": "This is science in progress,"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 762946.0,
      "end_time": 766780.0,
      "text": "and to solve the mystery, we need more data,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 766780.0,
      "end_time": 771396.0,
      "text": "and hopefully, the LHC will soon add new clues"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 771396.0,
      "end_time": 774017.0,
      "text": "to this story."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 774017.0,
      "end_time": 777847.0,
      "text": "Just one number, the Higgs boson mass,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 777847.0,
      "end_time": 783176.0,
      "text": "and yet, out of this number we learn so much."
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 783176.0,
      "end_time": 786223.0,
      "text": "I started from a hypothesis, that the known particles"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 786223.0,
      "end_time": 788259.0,
      "text": "are all there is in the universe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 788259.0,
      "end_time": 790965.0,
      "text": "even beyond the domain explored so far."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 790965.0,
      "end_time": 794733.0,
      "text": "From this, we discovered that the Higgs field"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 794733.0,
      "end_time": 798176.0,
      "text": "that permeates space-time may be standing"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 798176.0,
      "end_time": 802733.0,
      "text": "on a knife edge, ready for cosmic collapse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 802733.0,
      "end_time": 806283.0,
      "text": "and we discovered that this may be a hint"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 806283.0,
      "end_time": 810316.0,
      "text": "that our universe is only a grain of sand"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 810316.0,
      "end_time": 813929.0,
      "text": "in a giant beach, the multiverse."
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 813929.0,
      "end_time": 817180.0,
      "text": "But I don&#39;t know if my hypothesis is right."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 817180.0,
      "end_time": 820863.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s how physics works: A single measurement"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 820863.0,
      "end_time": 823727.0,
      "text": "can put us on the road to a new understanding"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 823727.0,
      "end_time": 825390.0,
      "text": "of the universe"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 825390.0,
      "end_time": 828409.0,
      "text": "or it can send us down a blind alley."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 828409.0,
      "end_time": 830973.0,
      "text": "But whichever it turns out to be,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 830973.0,
      "end_time": 834165.0,
      "text": "there is one thing I&#39;m sure of:"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 834165.0,
      "end_time": 837514.0,
      "text": "The journey will be full of surprises."
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 837514.0,
      "end_time": 838887.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 838887.0,
      "end_time": 848887.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}